data.description: A nicely renovated townhouse is waiting for you to call home.  New paint throughout the house.  Updated kitchen cabinets and granite countertops, and much more.  Newly replaced condenser and evaporator.  It's close to all major freeways and international food and within distance of schools.  High and dry during Harvey.
